# mdfind

> List files matching a given query
> More information: https://ss64.com/osx/mdfind.html

- Find a file by its name:

`mdfind -name {file some description}`

- Find a file by its content:

`mdfind "{string some description: query}"`

- Find a file containing a string, in a specific directory:

`mdfind -onlyin {directory some description} "{string some description: query}"`
